measurements.description: Eighteen flowers and nine buds on three upright mature inflorescences, one flower and seven buds on one immature inflorescence, inflorescences ranging from 91-98cm; nicely displayed on a clean 154-cm tall by 93-cm wide plant grown in bark, 30-cm plastic pot; sepals and petals white, lightly bushed coerulea, lateral sepals midline flushed darker coerulea; lip white flushed coerulea, throat light chartreuse, veined darker blue-purple; column white, anther cap purple; substance firm; texture bold crystalline.
